"v./n.试验，测定 【英】 n./v. 试验, 测定(testing of metals for quality ) 【例】 make an assay of an ore n. /v. 化验分析(物质的定性或定量分析, 尤指矿石或药物) 【例】The ore assays high in gold 这矿石经分析证明含金量很高. 【记】as正如, say说. 正如说的那样含金量很高－化验分析assay需要用essay短文来证明 【记】近于essay 评论；as+say 一边测试，分析（成份）一边说；analyse 分析 assay (v.)  c.1300, ""to try, endeavor, strive; test the quality of,"" from Anglo-French assaier, from assai (n.), from Old French essai ""trial"" (see essay). assay (n.)  ""trial, test of quality, test of character,"" mid-14c., from Anglo-French assai (see assay (v.)). Meaning ""analysis"" is from late 14c."
